sentences.sContent: All the muscles, viscera, nerves and ligaments are there in plain sight, but they’re still and lifeless.
sentences.sContent_eng: All the muscles, viscera, nerves and ligaments are there in plain sight, but they’re still and lifeless.
sentences.sCn: 虽然还有大量的肌肉，内脏，神经，韧带，但是他们却不能动。

sentences.sContent: Article 4 Quarantine inspection and supervision shall be conducted pursuant to this Law over trunks, heads and viscera of slaughtered animals.
sentences.sContent_eng: Article 4 Quarantine inspection and supervision shall be conducted pursuant to this Law over trunks, heads and viscera of slaughtered animals.
sentences.sCn: 第四条动物屠宰，依照本法对其胴体、头、蹄和内脏实施检疫、监督。

trans.tranOther: the large organs inside your body, such as your heart, lungs, and stomach
